{"tid":547951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國：拉美國家別過分依賴中國","createTime":"2018-02-02T04:26:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T13:10:32.000Z","uid":147314,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fb76d90e92281ca794a73e362097bfbefbc82318","tid":547951,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T04:26:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201802020026-1.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201802020026-1.aspx&d=t38vdQYCPkB44LpmfOizJf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=7cc31d04\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201802020026-1.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n（中央社德州奧斯汀1日綜合外電報導）美國國務卿提勒森今天警告，中國和俄羅斯在拉丁美洲扮演的角色「令人擔憂」，稱拉美不需要新帝國強權，他敦促拉美國家別過分依賴與中國的經濟關係，反而該與美國合作。<br />\n<br />\n法新社和路透社報導，提勒森（Rex Tillerson）將赴墨西哥、阿根廷、秘魯、哥倫比亞及牙買加展開6天訪問，出訪前在德州大學奧斯汀分校（University of Texas at Austin）演說。"},{"pid":"e67af21f23c39a9809d7e9a2122ebdb1ba9d7551","tid":547951,"uid":147314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T04:26:52.000Z","msg":"提勒森說：「中國今日逐漸在拉丁美洲立足，利用經濟治術拉攏這個區域，問題在於代價為何。」<br />\n<br />\n提勒森表示，中國現在已是智利、阿根廷、巴西及秘魯的最大貿易夥伴，還說必須要有強健的制度和負責任的政府，以免主權可能遭蠶食鯨吞。<br />\n<br />\n提勒森說：「這貿易帶來好處，但許多中國人採取不公平的貿易做法，也已損害這些國家的製造業，且造成失業及拉低勞工薪資。」<br />\n<br />\n他說：「拉丁美洲不需要只為他們自家人謀利的新帝國強權。中國的國家主導發展模式令人想起昔日。不一定要是這個半球掌控未來。」"},{"pid":"1ed9e134b4ca501891077e4bdb8d3441c3a9062a","tid":547951,"uid":147314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T04:27:21.000Z","msg":"提勒森還表示，俄羅斯持續在拉美區域加強布局，也同樣令人擔憂，他指控俄國持續把武器和軍備賣給「未共享或尊重民主價值」的不友善政府。<br />\n<br />\n他說：「我們的區域務必勤於防範那些未體現本區共同基本價值的遠方強權。」<br />\n<br />\n「美國是強烈的對比。我們不尋求收益傾向一方的短期協議。」"},{"pid":"ab01d52ad4c88699abfde033d7df85f5af6b792b","tid":547951,"uid":104213,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T04:29:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">稱拉美不需要新帝國強權，不該與美國合作。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b887a1221488c5fce8c3b1263b7490dab4d5db","tid":547951,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T04:29:51.000Z","msg":"美國務卿拉攏拉美 批中俄是新帝國強權<br />\n<br />\n發稿時間：2018/02/02 09:01最新更新：2018/02/02 09:01"},{"pid":"9bc70769780baedfa06548fd3b75c132f060f5cc","tid":547951,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T06:04:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"943afe7c27cd26534f6922e732db8d3db3a18936","tid":547951,"uid":24140,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"98b887a1221488c5fce8c3b1263b7490dab4d5db","tid":547951,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T04:29:51.000Z","msg":"美國務卿拉攏拉美 批中俄是新帝國強權<br />\n<br />\n發稿時間：2018/02/02 09:01最新更新：2018/02/02 09:01"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T06:14:29.000Z","msg":"對上幾次美國咁講時係納德同蘇聯<br />\nWell.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df2083658ef510bec368e1cc751c9df7d6316b8e","tid":547951,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T06:16:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a80ad781ffe8ffbd5caa3945f1ef927a0301b3e","tid":547951,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T06:16:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc38430cf79355c67181938ef511cb7a86686856","tid":547951,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T06:16:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34763496958436c61f21214da1bf6cf92adefca","tid":547951,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T06:17:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fcce49bfb40f2a324ed6c44253b81653560cbbaa","tid":547951,"uid":85163,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T06:19:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d73b7e19c7855598119e77ce2b6f8e76b08d32c","tid":547951,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote